General.Name: Thunderful Group AB
General.Description: Thunderful Group AB develops, publishes, and invests in games. It operates through two segments, Thunderful Games and Thunderful Distribution. The Thunderful Games segment develops, publishes, and invests in games. The Thunderful Distribution segment distributes games, game consoles, gaming accessories, and toys. The company was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.

2.Name: Mr. Agostino  Simonetta
2.Title: Chief Strategy and Investment Officer, Chief Games Officer & Head of Thunderful Games
